Package org.agreement_technologies.service.map_dtg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DTGData
    DTGData class represents the data that agents can exchange, i.e. value transitions for a variable, during the Domain Transitions Graph building.
    DTGFactoryImp
    DTGFactoryImp class creates the set of Domain Transition Graphs (one per variable) from the grounded task.
    DTGImp
    DTGImp class represents a Domain Transition Graph of a variable.
    DTGRequestImp
    DTGRequest interface is a request for information needed to build the Domain Transition Graphs in a distributed way.
    DTGSetImp
    DTGSetImp class represents a set of Domain Transition Graphs (one DTG per variable).
